name: Babygirl
description: Babygirl is a whimsical character from Matt Furie’s Cortex Vortex, capturing the surreal, playful energy that defines Furie’s artistic universe. Recognizable by her signature scarf and expressive design, she embodies the charm and weirdness of Matt Furie’s earlier works like Tuff Crowd and Doble Fried, now inspiring a new creative movement through the Babygirl token.The Babygirl Token celebrates creativity and community, bringing her story to life through the art of digital expression.
